node.text: Take a moment to be present and celebrate YOU!!!! I am just so damn proud of me! I have worked so hard for these past two years. Spiritually, emotionally, mentally, and physically!!! From serious postpartum depression to heartbreak, depression, confusion, desperation, emotions, doubts and so much fear I felt I was drowning. I promise you tho all things are truly possible through God, your village, faith and determination. This is what it’s like to be human. Ups and downs. DO NOT feed into those negative voices in your head. Please stay focused ✨ stay hungry! Stay patient. Don’t take that leap of faith honey, you better jump!!! This life is literally whatever you want to make it!! Embrace the pain. Let that shit fuel you!!!! Yes…it’s easier said than done but you gotta start by saying it and CLAIMING it! This message is for whoever needs it ❤️ Sending mad love and positive vibrations ya’ll way ✨✨✨✨
